Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're talking like that, have you seen Masakazu Tamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.00,0:18:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.00,0:18:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been living behind my house for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is it like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of them, but you can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy, he'd walk in front of our house and dump it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.00,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.00,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it then, or are you alone, or is there someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Masakazu Tamura
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know, I haven't seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been about a year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of them, but I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.00,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Tokoro-san and others, but I can't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm not going to meet you, so either way
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, you know, I've been alone for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call you sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no, but
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was eating at an Okinawan restaurant the other night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. No one else has
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.00,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm about to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm having dinner alone at an Okinawan restaurant."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I found an Okinawan restaurant by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm alone at the far end of the restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was eating a set of Australian night jumpers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.00,0:19:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also drinking a little armoire and I'm on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to feel a little bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I called Hamada, and I asked him if he'd like to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But well, I got an answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's living like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one of them already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting married?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting married.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Remarried?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not remarry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.00,0:20:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say it straight out and right away
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to say it, you know, when you ask
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you who I'm dating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.00,0:20:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get married, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.00,0:20:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because my child is only 9 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to be able to do it until he's a little older.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say that, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.00,0:20:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he says it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it about time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.00,0:20:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.00,0:20:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying no, like a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When are you going to let me see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.00,0:20:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How many people are you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a time of year, so it's like a two-timing thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really not doing it, and it would be a disaster if I went that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even know what I'm talking about, Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to fly like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how it works, there's only one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really that worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka is one of those people that you don't hear from the convivia in the face of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But some times, I mean once or twice, Tanaka's family
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going out to dinner with you and the kids, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,They bathe me, this kid here, my kid there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you very much, Endo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I like it so much, endo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the ho ho ho ho
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm happy, this is
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I come home from work and I really love my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Endo, I love that you said you had a ho ho ho ho today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr.Endo, I love that you did Hohohoi today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.00,0:21:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever see anything like that? When your children were small, Matsumoto's children...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I met him when he was very small, at a school like NGK in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm probably the first person to say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm bringing him to a film festival here in Okinawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was there for the first time, at Matsumoto-san's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with Matsumoto-san's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being totally ignored.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you've been ignored?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was already standing there, so I said hello or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I kind of bumped it a little bit, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a little red.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.00,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have been nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.00,0:22:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still tiny, and he's a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, to top it all off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he goes to daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.00,0:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he doing to his dad now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've met him, you've seen him once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.00,0:22:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no. I just thought it looked red.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, "What's wrong? I said, "What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He looked at me for a second, and then he just said, "Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.00,0:22:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm talking about, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.00,0:22:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, all the guys did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, it's just the way it's handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.00,0:23:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it is, my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When she was little, when she was about Missy or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada used to take me to dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.00,0:23:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's basically a very friendly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,When Hamada says come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.00,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She started crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.00,0:23:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you cry, I didn't cry at that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My boy, he said it with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's Machan, Yamachan, En-chan and Hamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a 3- or 4-year-old kid like Machan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you understand, that kind of thing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you know, Machan and I watch TV and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.00,0:23:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Machan, Yama-chan, En-san, Hamada-san
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.00,0:23:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san with three attachments
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying anything, of course, my mom
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.00,0:23:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let him say Hama-chan already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let him say "Hama-chan" right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.00,0:23:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He don't know if he's allowed to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.00,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He thought you knew what you were doing, even as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't say Hama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid is not that cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me just say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hama-san
